headline: Is It Worth Investing in Deere (DE) Based on Wall Street's Bullish Views?
summary: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for Deere (DE) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?

headline: ‘It goes too far’: Robby Starbuck SHRM panel legitimizes anti-DEI stance, stakeholders say
summary: Many in the industry say platforming the conservative influencer — who has called DEI “poison” — continues to take SHRM in the wrong direction.
